      "body" : "Disclaimer: these were quick hacks to see what it would take to build on non-x86, I'd prefer a change that's a little more obvious. Mind testing this instead of the first chunk?\r\n\r\n```diff\r\ndiff --git a/depends/Makefile b/depends/Makefile\r\nindex 0ddd348e53..14e94ba453 100644\r\n--- a/depends/Makefile\r\n+++ b/depends/Makefile\r\n@@ -21,7 +21,6 @@ BUILD_ID_SALT ?= salt\r\n host:=$(BUILD)\r\n ifneq ($(HOST),)\r\n host:=$(HOST)\r\n-host_toolchain:=$(HOST)-\r\n endif\r\n\r\n ifneq ($(DEBUG),)\r\ndiff --git a/depends/hosts/default.mk b/depends/hosts/default.mk\r\nindex 6f60d6b3fd..144e5f88b7 100644\r\n--- a/depends/hosts/default.mk\r\n+++ b/depends/hosts/default.mk\r\n@@ -1,3 +1,7 @@\r\n+ifneq ($(host),$(build))\r\n+host_toolchain:=$(host)-\r\n+endif\r\n+\r\n default_host_CC = $(host_toolchain)gcc\r\n default_host_CXX = $(host_toolchain)g++\r\n default_host_AR = $(host_toolchain)ar\r\n```",
